@page "/solutions/sales"
@layout MarketingLayout

<PageTitle>NavTour for Sales — Close Deals Faster with Interactive Demos</PageTitle>
<HeadContent>
    <meta name="description" content="Send personalized interactive demos after every discovery call. Track engagement, prioritize follow-ups, and close deals 40% faster." />
</HeadContent>

<section class="mkt-section" style="padding-bottom:var(--space-16)">
    <div class="mkt-container" style="max-width:680px">
        <p class="mkt-eyebrow text-center">For Sales Teams</p>
        <h1 class="text-center" style="margin-top:var(--space-2)">Close deals faster with interactive demos</h1>
        <p class="text-center" style="margin-top:var(--space-5)">Prospects go cold waiting for live demos. Send personalized interactive experiences within minutes of a discovery call — and track every interaction.</p>
        <div class="mkt-hero-actions" style="justify-content:center;margin-top:var(--space-8)">
            <a href="/register" class="mkt-btn mkt-btn-primary mkt-btn-lg">Start Free</a>
            <a href="/contact" class="mkt-btn mkt-btn-secondary mkt-btn-lg">Talk to Sales</a>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>

@* Post-Discovery *@
<section class="mkt-section">
    <div class="mkt-container reveal">
        <div class="mkt-grid mkt-grid-2" style="align-items:center;gap:var(--space-16)">
            <div>
                <p class="mkt-eyebrow">Post-Discovery</p>
                <h2 style="margin-top:var(--space-2)">Send a personalized demo in under 2 minutes</h2>
                <p style="margin-top:var(--space-4)">After a discovery call, your prospect is at peak interest. Don't waste that momentum scheduling a follow-up. With NavTour, reps select a demo template, personalize it with the prospect's company name and use case, and share a link — all before the prospect has time to forget the conversation.</p>
                <ul class="mkt-benefits">
                    <li>Select from pre-built demo templates by vertical</li>
                    <li>Auto-personalize with prospect name and company via URL tokens</li>
                    <li>Share via link, email, or embed in follow-up sequences</li>
                </ul>
            </div>
            <div class="mkt-placeholder mkt-placeholder-feature">Personalized demo with prospect branding</div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>

@* Pre-Call Prep *@
<section class="mkt-section-alt">
    <div class="mkt-container reveal">
        <div class="mkt-grid mkt-grid-2" style="align-items:center;gap:var(--space-16)">
            <div class="mkt-placeholder mkt-placeholder-feature">Engagement analytics showing step completion</div>
            <div>
                <p class="mkt-eyebrow">Pre-Call Intelligence</p>
                <h2 style="margin-top:var(--space-2)">Know exactly what your prospect cares about</h2>
                <p style="margin-top:var(--space-4)">Before your next call, see exactly which demo steps the prospect viewed, where they spent the most time, and which sections they revisited. Use engagement data to tailor your pitch and skip the features they've already explored in depth.</p>
                <ul class="mkt-benefits">
                    <li>Step-by-step engagement timeline per viewer</li>
                    <li>Time-on-step metrics reveal feature interest</li>
                    <li>Drop-off analysis identifies objection points</li>
                </ul>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>

@* Champion Enablement *@
<section class="mkt-section">
    <div class="mkt-container reveal">
        <div class="mkt-grid mkt-grid-2" style="align-items:center;gap:var(--space-16)">
            <div>
                <p class="mkt-eyebrow">Champion Enablement</p>
                <h2 style="margin-top:var(--space-2)">Give champions a demo they can share internally</h2>
                <p style="margin-top:var(--space-4)">Multi-stakeholder deals stall when your champion can't effectively communicate your value to decision-makers. Give them a polished, interactive demo they can forward to their CFO, CTO, or procurement team — no additional sales calls required.</p>
                <ul class="mkt-benefits">
                    <li>Shareable links that work without login or setup</li>
                    <li>Track who else in the organization views the demo</li>
                    <li>Multiple viewer tracking for multi-thread deals</li>
                </ul>
            </div>
            <div class="mkt-placeholder mkt-placeholder-feature">Champion sharing demo with buying committee</div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>

@* Deal Acceleration *@
<section class="mkt-section-alt">
    <div class="mkt-container reveal">
        <div class="mkt-grid mkt-grid-2" style="align-items:center;gap:var(--space-16)">
            <div class="mkt-placeholder mkt-placeholder-feature">Deal dashboard with engagement scores</div>
            <div>
                <p class="mkt-eyebrow">Deal Acceleration</p>
                <h2 style="margin-top:var(--space-2)">Prioritize deals with engagement data</h2>
                <p style="margin-top:var(--space-4)">Not all deals are equal. NavTour's engagement scoring shows you which prospects are most engaged — who's viewed the demo multiple times, who's shared it internally, and who's exploring your most valuable features. Focus your time on deals that are most likely to close.</p>
                <ul class="mkt-benefits">
                    <li>Engagement scoring per prospect and account</li>
                    <li>Multi-viewer tracking for buying committee signals</li>
                    <li>CRM integration for pipeline prioritization</li>
                </ul>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>

@* Metrics *@
<section class="mkt-section">
    <div class="mkt-container text-center reveal">
        <h2>Sales teams using NavTour see results</h2>
        <div class="mkt-grid mkt-grid-3" style="margin-top:var(--space-10)">
            <MetricCard Value="40%" Label="faster deal cycles" Source="vs. live-demo-only workflows" />
            <MetricCard Value="67%" Label="fewer no-shows" Source="prospects who interact before a call" />
            <MetricCard Value="35%" Label="higher close rate" Source="with personalized interactive demos" />
        </div>
    </div>
</section>

@* Testimonial *@
<section class="mkt-section-alt">
    <div class="mkt-container reveal">
        <TestimonialCard Featured="true"
            Quote="NavTour cut our time-to-demo from 3 days to 5 minutes. Our close rate is up 35% since we started sending personalized demos after every discovery call."
            Name="James Whitfield"
            Title="Sales Director"
            Company="Pinnacle SaaS"
            Metric="35%"
            MetricLabel="increase in close rate" />
    </div>
</section>

<CtaSection Title="Ready to close deals faster?" Subtitle="Start sending interactive demos today. Free to start, no credit card required." />
